item.title: Help! JAVA ERROR!
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

Uninstall your 64-bit JRE, and install the 32 bit version instead.
For some reason, the walking algorithm in our deobfuscated clients don’t get along well with the 64-bit JVM.

Read full topic
